aces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地係朋友圈推得好行，但好似冇咩local留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日科大，明日七大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84968c8217ea0a157c3c9dfd4c1331279737014d","tid":1645242,"uid":199902,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:36:02.000Z","msg":"但係黎明終將降臨<br />\n冇至撚黑暗嘅黑夜，就唔會有對光輝黎明嘅渴望同珍惜<br />\n我哋終有一日會喺煲底相認、相擁，因為我哋只可以勝利，同埋係一定會勝利"},{"pid":"ac51051910482d220df1cfd8af187a06b5466a12","tid":1645242,"uid":43751,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:36:24.000Z","msg":"一直同朋友講 查案係多撚餘<br />\n如果有受害者 身邊人都會出聲<br />\n仲有香港 本身就好多人自殺<br />\n只係因為查案先關心自殺既人"},{"pid":"1271927b94c89b30616676c243a032f10da7e5f9","tid":1645242,"uid":43751,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:37:50.000Z","msg":"但講真 連續兩日有車撞人 攞命<br />\n政府 差佬 新聞 全部都擋睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n深夜捉走個人 又有幾出奇"},{"pid":"71608695b6c752b703726ef547f470d7aad317f3","tid":1645242,"uid":78971,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:39:45.000Z","msg":"估唔到香港都有今日<br />\n政府上上下下都係大話精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae11280f1842fd656070551ada33bc91a2b4c33d","tid":1645242,"uid":43751,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:44:27.000Z","msg":"早兩個月仲光復元朗<br />\n打死都唔撚信 會跳海自殺啦<br />\n全裸<br />\n無遺書<br />\n失蹤<br />\n老母男友是狗<br />\n<br />\n要死都揀跳樓啦"},{"pid":"e35397464ce99194e42b0acdc17e4cb436ea4ca9","tid":1645242,"uid":43751,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:45:46.000Z","msg":"成部車撞入人群<br />\n外國就叫恐襲<br />\n香港可以有獎金收<br />\n屌你老母咩"},{"pid":"4009d03dc082e3701943a9d22d47a5d73e097f3d","tid":1645242,"uid":34295,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T22:46:40.000Z","msg":"咁你要